{"tid":2437683,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來比人呃左咁耐","createTime":"2021-03-08T04:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T07:14:15.000Z","uid":252732,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5772e2a5abfc4c7591f91b3ba11972645a1ffd3b","tid":2437683,"uid":252732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:28:26.000Z","msg":"話說有個frd之前同佢食親飯都帶得$80 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次食親放題都要我幫佢墊底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫佢大大話話比左八九次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知佢屋企做小生意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以為佢屋企都唔係有錢 所以都肯幫佢比下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係點知佢今日同我講 近排屋企生意好差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日都係搵得一萬蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我即刻嚇一嚇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗咁你屋企咪一個搵成三十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我當你扣埋鋪租成本至少都賺十萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢仲要話疫情下生意少咗一半 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁即係平時佢屋企都賺緊廿萬一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解仲呃我個幾百蚊食飯錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b1af5deee4ffeed0063813ddd70fefda95fb1ef","tid":2437683,"uid":134087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:30:25.000Z","msg":"量入為出<br />\n好仔嚟，唔係敗曬屋企啲身家<br />\nbtw, 感情台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf4a3eeddf2f0b225667ffb6cc2f8d7654ad774","tid":2437683,"uid":176282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T04:30:46.000Z","msg":"唔係你估佢點揾咁多"},{"pid":"43837cfe0332ed659468a3af32b1834ae2747f5f","tid":2437683,"uid":252732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1b1af5deee4ffeed0063813ddd70fefda95fb1ef","tid":2437683,"uid":134087,"